- [ ] 404 + error-handling middleware, process-level error listeners
- [ ] Schema validation for every route; JSON body size limit
- [ ] `helmet`, strict CORS allowlist, rate limiting, `x-powered-by` disabled
- [ ] AuthN/AuthZ on `/users`; minimize returned PII
- [ ] Env-driven port, graceful shutdown on `SIGTERM`/`SIGINT`
- [ ] Async handler wrapper (or Express 5)
- [ ] Structured logger with header/body redaction

