  const id = Number(req.params.id);
  if (!Number.isInteger(id) || id <= 0 || id > 1e9) {
    return res.status(400).json({ error: 'Invalid id' });
  }
  // ... lookup
});
```

### 6. No body-size limit / JSON parser hardening
If you add `app.use(express.json())`, cap the payload size to prevent DoS:

