| Errors | Centralized 404 + error middleware | Uniform responses; no stack-trace leakage |
| PII | Drop `email` from default response | Principle of least disclosure |
| Config | `process.env.PORT` | 12-factor; avoid hardcoded ports in prod |
| Fingerprinting | `disable('x-powered-by')` | Removes Express advertising header |
| Lifecycle | `server.close()` on SIGTERM/SIGINT | Clean shutdown, drains connections |
| Robustness | `unhandledRejection` / `uncaughtException` handlers | Fail loudly, exit safely |

