2. Add `helmet`, `express-rate-limit`, disable `x-powered-by`, configure CORS.
3. Require auth + pagination on `/users`; drop `email` from the default projection.
4. Move port to env; add graceful shutdown.
5. Adopt `zod`/`joi` now so future routes have a validation pattern to follow.
6. Replace `console.*` with a structured logger; scrub sensitive fields.

